name: Bay 2012 calendar
description:
Proudly we present our very own 2012 calendar.
We felt need for a good, cheap calendar. So we made our own!
We made a random selection out of birthdays of inspirational people and several events throughout the year, whose dates we added to the calendar.  Please feel free to add your own data to the calendar as well.

- Designed by Bay.
- Handy lay-out with special notes section for every month. 
- Special birthdays and events highlighted.

Please visit our website for a detailed look: http://www.baycreatives.net/

Price excl. shipping.
